title: Jose Mourinho insists Manchester United didn’t lose to Hull (Video)
text:
Jose Mourinho insists Manchester United didn’t lose to Hull (Video) By Paul Morrissey   Man United lose at Hull, but reach EFL Cup final 
It was a bittersweet night for Manchester United in Hull, as they lost to the minnows on the night, but still managed to qualify for the EFL Cup final, by virtue of their 1st leg win. 
United won the first leg at Old Trafford 2-0, so they still managed to squeeze into the final, despite losing 2-1 at Hull in the 2nd leg. 
Or did they ? ‘We didn’t lose’ 
Because according to Jose Mourinho, Manchester United didn’t lose, and they remain ‘unbeatable.’ 
As far as the Portuguese is concerned, the game finished 1-1, as he didn’t see Hull’s first goal (a petty protest about Hull’s dubious penalty ). Loading tags...
